title: Railworks TS2015 - Virtual Railroads DB Class 151 Bundle
description:
Railworks TS2015 - Virtual Railroads DB Class 151 Bundle

The package contains the freightloco DB Class 151 in green. blue-beige, orientred and trafficred. 
One loco has the number belonging to the loco and the colour the second loco has a dynamic number.

    BR151 green
    BR151 dynamic number green
    BR151 bluebeige
    BR151 dynamic number bluebeige
    BR151 orientred
    BR151 dynamic number orientred
    BR151 trafficred
    BR151 dynamic number trafficred
